Sounds like your throttle shaft holes are worn and need to be  re-bushed.  
I notice you are in the UK, so this may not be practical for  you.  In the 
States, I would send my carb to RIMCO (_http://www.rimcovw.com/_ 
(http://www.rimcovw.com/) ), to get the the  throttle shafts re-bushed.
